dct_title_s: West Indies, anchorages in Saint Lucia (Raster Image)
dct_description_sm: Prepared and published by the National Imagery and Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours, hachures, and spot heights. "From a British Admiralty chart of 1990." "Copyright 1997 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Components: A. Port of Castries. Scale 1:5,010 -- B. Vieux Fort. Scale 1:20,049 -- C. Grand Cul de Sac Bay. Scale 1:10,050 -- D. Marigot Harbour. Scale 1:5,013. Includes tidal information. Map No. 25528.
This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
